HEADWORD: Petroline
<hw>Pet"ro*line</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>A paraffin obtained from petroleum from Rangoon in India, and
practically identical with ordinary paraffin.</def>⟦br⟧
